step
label "Start Pets"
To earn this achievement, you will need to defeat every Pet Battle Master Tamer in the Broken Isles using a full Magic team
|tip Make sure, when fighting each pet battle master, all 3 of your pet slots are Magic type pets.
|tip These Pet Battle Master Tamers can not be challenged when they are not a World Quest.
|tip Only 3 Pet Battle World Quests are up per daily reset and, once challenged and defeated on one character, they can not be challenged again on that character.
|tip To complete this achievement, you will need many different level 25 Magic pets. Strategies will be provided with each step, giving the best known set up to defeat each Master.
|tip If you need help collecting any of the pets suggested, we have guides for all of them.
|tip You can check out these guides by pressing SHIFT-P, then going to the Pet Journal tab, press the Zygor Icon next to any pet to open that guide up.
